breeds.name: Norwegian Forest Cat
breeds.temperament: Sweet, Active, Intelligent, Social, Playful, Lively, Curious
breeds.description: The Norwegian Forest Cat is a sweet, loving cat. She appreciates praise and loves to interact with her parent. She makes a loving companion and bonds with her parents once she accepts them for her own. She is still a hunter at heart. She loves to chase toys as if they are real. She is territorial and patrols several times each day to make certain that all is fine.
breeds.alt_names: Skogkatt / Skaukatt, Norsk Skogkatt / Norsk Skaukatt, Weegie

She makes a loving companion and bonds with her parents once she accepts them for her own. She is still a hunter at heart. She loves to chase toys as if they are real. She is territorial and patrols several times each day to make certain that all is fine.
breeds.alt_names: Skogkatt / Skaukatt, Norsk Skogkatt / Norsk Skaukatt, Weegie
